data.description: Nice 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in Inverness Highlands. This home offers an open split floor plan, a bright and inviting living area with vaulted ceilings and and plenty of natural light. Most recent updates include a new water heater, new roof in 2016 and a new A/C in 2015. The backyard is fenced and offers a serene area for relaxing, gardening or plenty of room for a shed. This area is convenient to downtown Inverness for local shopping, restaurants, medical, and the 46 mile paved Withlacoochee trail. Enjoy the warm and sunny Florida weather all year long.
